---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import HeroSection from '../components/HeroSection.astro';
---

<Layout title="Frequently Asked Questions - A&H Solutions">
  <Header />
  <main>
    <HeroSection 
      title="Frequently Asked Questions" 
      highlightText="Questions"
      description="Find answers to common questions about our custom development services and how we can help your business."
    />
    
    <section class="py-16 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800">
      <div class="container-custom">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <!-- FAQ Categories Navigation -->
          <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-4 mb-12">
            <a href="#services" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-primary-200 dark:hover:bg-primary-800 transition-colors">
              Services
            </a>
            <a href="#process" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Development Process
            </a>
            <a href="#pricing" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Pricing & Timeline
            </a>
            <a href="#industries" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Industries
            </a>
            <a href="#support" class="px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 dark:hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">
              Support & Maintenance
            </a>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Services FAQs -->
          <div id="services" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-3 7h3m-3 4h3m-6-4h.01M9 16h.01"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Services & Solutions
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What services does A&H Solutions offer?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We specialize in custom software development including mobile app development, web app development, AI integrations & automation, data analytics & visualization, cloud solutions & integration, and IT consulting & advisory services. Each solution is tailored to your specific business requirements and industry needs.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you only work with startups?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  No—we work with both startups and enterprises. While we specialize in helping startups succeed where 90% fail, we also provide enterprise-grade solutions for established businesses looking to modernize their technology stack or launch new digital initiatives.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Can you integrate AI into my existing product?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes—our team designs custom AI integrations that enhance performance and user experience. We can add AI capabilities like automation, predictive analytics, natural language processing, and machine learning to existing applications or build new AI-powered solutions from scratch.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you provide both web and mobile app development?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Absolutely! We develop both web applications and mobile apps (iOS and Android). We can also create cross-platform solutions using frameworks like React Native or Flutter to maximize efficiency and maintain consistency across platforms.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Process FAQs -->
          <div id="process" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Development Process
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What is your development process?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We follow a structured approach: Discovery & Planning → Design & Prototyping → Development & Testing → Deployment & Launch → Ongoing Support. We use agile methodology with regular client communication, milestone reviews, and iterative development to ensure your project stays on track.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How involved will I be in the development process?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  You'll be closely involved throughout the entire process. We provide regular updates, milestone demonstrations, and seek your feedback at key stages. We believe in transparent collaboration to ensure the final product perfectly matches your vision and requirements.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you provide project management?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we provide comprehensive project management as part of our service. You'll have a dedicated project manager who coordinates all aspects of development, maintains timelines, and serves as your primary point of contact throughout the project.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What technologies do you work with?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We work with modern, proven technologies including React, Node.js, Python, .NET, React Native, Flutter, AWS, Google Cloud, Azure, and various databases. We choose the best technology stack based on your specific requirements, scalability needs, and long-term goals.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Pricing & Timeline FAQs -->
          <div id="pricing" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Pricing & Timeline
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How do you price your projects?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Every project is unique, so we provide custom quotes based on your specific requirements, complexity, timeline, and technology stack. We'll provide a detailed proposal with transparent pricing after our initial consultation and requirements analysis. No hidden costs—just honest, upfront pricing.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How long does a typical project take?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Project timelines vary based on complexity and scope. Simple apps might take 2-3 months, while complex enterprise solutions can take 6-12 months or more. We provide realistic timeline estimates during our initial consultation and keep you informed of progress throughout development.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you offer payment plans?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we offer flexible payment structures tied to project milestones. Typically, this includes an initial deposit, payments at key development milestones, and final payment upon completion. This helps manage cash flow while ensuring project progress.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">How do you keep costs low without losing quality?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We use smart architecture, AI-driven workflow optimization, and efficient engineering practices to cut infrastructure waste—often saving clients thousands per month while delivering enterprise-grade quality. We focus on building scalable, maintainable solutions that reduce long-term costs.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Industries FAQs -->
          <div id="industries" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Industries & Specializations
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What industries do you work with?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We work across diverse industries including healthcare, finance, e-commerce, real estate, insurance, legal services, education, manufacturing, hospitality, wellness, and more. Each industry has unique requirements and regulations, which we understand and incorporate into our solutions.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you handle industry-specific compliance requirements?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Absolutely. We have experience with various compliance requirements including HIPAA (healthcare), SOX and PCI DSS (finance), GDPR and CCPA (data privacy), and industry-specific regulations. We build compliance into the architecture from day one, not as an afterthought.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Can you build solutions for highly regulated industries?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we specialize in building compliant solutions for regulated industries. Whether it's financial services requiring bank-level security, healthcare applications needing HIPAA compliance, or legal software requiring confidentiality protections, we understand and implement the necessary safeguards.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What if my industry isn't listed?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  We work across many more industries than we list on our website. Our approach is to understand your specific business requirements, industry challenges, and regulatory environment to create tailored solutions. Contact us to discuss your unique industry needs.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Support FAQs -->
          <div id="support" class="mb-16">
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-8 flex items-center">
              <span class="inline-block rounded-full bg-primary-100 dark:bg-primary-900 p-2 mr-3">
                <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                  <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M18.364 5.636l-3.536 3.536m0 5.656l3.536 3.536M9.172 9.172L5.636 5.636m3.536 9.192l-3.536 3.536M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-5 0a4 4 0 11-8 0 4 4 0 018 0z"></path>
                </svg>
              </span>
              Support & Maintenance
            </h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you provide ongoing support and maintenance?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we offer comprehensive post-launch support including bug fixes, security updates, performance monitoring, and feature enhancements. We provide various support packages to match your needs, from basic maintenance to full ongoing development partnerships.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">What happens after my project launches?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Post-launch, we monitor your application's performance, provide technical support, and can help with ongoing feature development. We're invested in your long-term success and can scale our support based on your evolving needs.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Do you provide training for our team?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Absolutely! We provide comprehensive training for your team on how to use and manage your new system. This includes administrator training, user guides, and ongoing support to ensure your team can effectively utilize all features.
                </p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="card p-6 border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-3">Can you help us scale our application as we grow?</h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300">
                  Yes, we build applications with scalability in mind from the start. As your business grows, we can help optimize performance, add new features, integrate additional services, and ensure your technology infrastructure supports your expansion plans.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="text-center mt-16">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Still have questions?</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-8">
              Our team is here to help. Contact us and we'll get back to you within 24 hours with a detailed response.
            </p>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Get Your Questions Answered</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>